  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the illness experience of patients with keratoconus as well as the rubbing habits of
      this population compared to the general population. To do this, the investigators used a
      questionnaire made by a Bordeaux team with questions on the experience of the patients'
      illness, their management and their friction habits
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
